WEBVTT

00:00.139 --> 00:01.389
Hello, can I help you?

00:02.335 --> 00:04.513
Hi, I'm looking for a coat.

00:05.875 --> 00:07.121
What kind are you looking for?

00:07.953 --> 00:11.184
Something nice and warm.

00:12.222 --> 00:13.467
How about this black coat?

00:13.999 --> 00:15.368
It's very popular right now.

00:16.541 --> 00:18.196
How much is it?

00:18.877 --> 00:20.249
It's $300.

00:20.726 --> 00:24.231
$300? That's too expensive for me.

00:24.560 --> 00:26.099
Do you have anything cheaper?

00:27.551 --> 00:28.974
Here's a brown coat.

00:29.301 --> 00:31.045
This one's $150.

00:31.469 --> 00:32.535
I love it!

00:33.381 --> 00:35.373
Do you have it in a bigger size?

00:35.881 --> 00:37.397
Sure. Here it is.

00:38.127 --> 00:40.927
I also need black shoes.

00:41.053 --> 00:42.236
Do you have any?

00:43.309 --> 00:46.356
We have ones on sale for $45.

00:46.782 --> 00:50.107
Awesome! I'd like them in size 10, please.

00:51.057 --> 00:53.918
OK. Would there be anything else?

00:54.911 --> 00:57.153
No, that would be all. Thanks.

00:58.123 --> 01:01.045
The total amount is $195.

01:01.555 --> 01:03.391
Are you paying in cash or credit card?

01:03.728 --> 01:06.402
Credit card. Here it is.

01:07.122 --> 01:08.311
Please sign here.

01:09.016 --> 01:10.972
Thank you so much.

01:11.843 --> 01:13.464
No problem. Have a great day!

